{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-10", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "無前", "storyInfo": "善人的布施，終將抵達大地的每一個角落。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g8_farnorthtundra_aurora", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "呼……呼……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "痛……石頭在肉裡瘋狂生長……幾乎能聽到聲音。為什麼我還沒死掉？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "沒有力氣，四肢不受控制……跑！往東跑！", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "往南是送死，往北也是送死。往西……如果遠北都出事了，西部那些礦場也不可能倖免。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但逃跑能逃出遠北嗎……又要逃去哪裡才能遠離痛苦？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯遠北邊界，荒野</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跑……不動……了……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就到，這裡……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-60", "duration": 0.7, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "感染者礦工"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊好像有人？", "name": "遠處的聲音"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去看看——", "name": "遠處的聲音"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，請讓我去吧……", "name": "遠處的聲音"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感覺到那只是一個受過許多苦痛的人。", "name": "遠處的聲音"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脫力、脫水，而且許久未曾進食……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是感染者。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳！", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同胞，他也是我們的同胞！", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您救救他吧，就像您救我們所有人一樣——", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再一次施行您的神蹟！", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是神蹟……唉。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦石病不是使他如此痛苦的主要原因，我只能讓他不再因疾病而疼痛，卻不能幫助他飽腹、給他喝乾淨的水、讓他有安全的地方入睡。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法施行神蹟，我並非全能，我只是……相信。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#4$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您總是這麼謙遜，我們都明白。", "name": "虔誠的聲音"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……先生，您還能聽見我說話嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我會握住您的手……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“相信吧。相信我們的生命。”", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“相信我們的身體與思維，相信我們心臟的每一次律動，相信我們肺葉的每一次收放。”", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“相信我們自身，是所有力量的來源。”", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從此，您不必在死亡的恐懼中殘喘。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "源石在體內迅速生長帶來的疼痛逐漸遠去。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他仍能聽見那些聲音，卻不再因此痛得輾轉反側。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——你是誰？", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你救了我……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳，咳——", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該怎麼，感謝你？", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#3$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以像這裡所有的兄弟姊妹一樣，稱呼我為“希爾達”。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神蹟——", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達再一次救了我們的同胞！", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她救了我們所有人，只是用母親一樣的撫摸，就像剛才一樣，抹去了所有的病痛！", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達！", "name": "急切的聲音"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達。", "name": "虔誠的聲音"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達！", "name": "許多人的聲音"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾達……希爾達。", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，那是我的名字。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你長什麼樣子？無論是你，還是其他說話的人，我都看不清楚……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的頭上有傷，是跑得太急，在哪裡跌倒了，因此撞破頭了嗎？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是腦中的瘀血讓您看不清楚。沒關係，我們可以攙扶著您……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請告訴我，您接下來想去哪裡？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道……", "name": "感染者礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就先跟我們一起吧。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要帶我們去一個沒有痛苦的地方，對不對？", "name": "虔誠的聲音"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，只要你們仍願意與我同行……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g9_seasurface_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要我們相信。", "name": "希爾達"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}